ygData.messageBody:
You just have to give one a copper peice. he will tell you "no this is
wrong, i need key XXX"

it works everytime. there will still be some keys that dont have a place to
go. i have no idea about those.

Lanh Lv15 Bard
Lanhdanan Lv18 Warrior
